{"tid":2362031,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［請大家關注SMA患者］ 柒婆又一謊言，They are dying.","createTime":"2021-01-11T07:23:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-12T17:17:53.000Z","uid":325346,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c989a7f6a5c24000f77a0f0a59eab22e7ae9f0d6","tid":2362031,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T07:23:23.000Z","msg":"兩年半前，行政長官親自與藥廠洽商，引入成人脊髓肌肉萎縮症（SMA）的藥物。所有SMA患者滿心歡喜，以為自己終於等到有藥醫，沒想到是空歡喜一場。<br />\n<br />\n我們有幸邀得鄭子誠先生聲音導航，講出一班SMA病友等藥的苦況。 <br />\n<br />\n兩年半以來，醫管局一直以「科研數據和臨床實證不足」為托詞，拒絕讓成年SMA患者用藥。罕盟建議政府推出「罕藥試用期」，讓所有合適的SMA患者都可試用。「試用期」結束後，政府資助有療效及有經濟需要的患者繼續用藥；無療效的停止用藥。<br />\n<br />\n此舉可令患者早日有藥用，並有利政府掌握臨床數據，增加與藥廠議價的優勢。<br />\n<br />\n雖然香港新冠肺炎仍未「清零」，醫管局工作很忙，但無人知道疫情何時會結束。SMA患者的命也是命！醫管局可不可以調派些少人手，與藥廠和病友會落實方案呢？<br />\n<br />\n請儘快給成年SMA患者一個治療的機會！"},{"pid":"613d5d38454d88ca985b7dd02c57a9ee6258e9b4","tid":2362031,"uid":325346,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T07:25:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/YX8m_JsYXW4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYX8m_JsYXW4&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2BWlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=a3247afa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/YX8m_JsYXW4</a><br />\n<br />\n結果而家得十個小朋友<br />\n同一個成年患者（影片中人）有藥用<br />\n<br />\n其實人等死<br />\n<br />\n點解佩珊有藥用，因為佢寫信俾柒婆同親自接見<br />\n<br />\n其他人無藥用就因為無柒婆可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee945a208bbaa4ecb8031706e7e3186895fa16c1","tid":2362031,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T07:27:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/RareDiseaseHK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2FRareDiseaseHK%2F&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2BWlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=eafbe255\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/RareDiseaseHK/</a><br />\n<br />\n大家去睇片去關注佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71ac3e70a1793528d16de75fedca11f888386ac8","tid":2362031,"uid":325346,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T11:38:14.000Z","msg":"自推<br />\n希望大家關心下<br />\n有幾十個後生成年人無藥用<br />\n無希望<br />\n<br />\n包括甜故作家游家敏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5df927ba1365ae0f3fab2750bc42b9e3344d568","tid":2362031,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T11:42:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5ce406a91dc822a7796576ab14d8712f8c49ce03","tid":2362031,"uid":325346,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T11:49:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lj.hkej.com/lj2017/artculture/article/id/2343028/【人物】「性勇武鬥士」游家敏+為殘疾人士性權發聲\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flj.hkej.com%2Flj2017%2Fartculture%2Farticle%2Fid%2F2343028%2F%E3%80%90%E4%BA%BA%E7%89%A9%E3%80%91%E3%80%8C%E6%80%A7%E5%8B%87%E6%AD%A6%E9%AC%A5%E5%A3%AB%E3%80%8D%E6%B8%B8%E5%AE%B6%E6%95%8F%2B%E7%82%BA%E6%AE%98%E7%96%BE%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB%E6%80%A7%E6%AC%8A%E7%99%BC%E8%81%B2&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2BWlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=b1c3d7df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lj.hkej.com/lj2017/artculture/article/id/2343028/【人物】「性勇武鬥士」游家敏+為殘疾人士性權發聲</a><br />\n<br />\n地方的咸故需要讀者"},{"pid":"2ce999f6c297b5b671f2f2471a37f6e7c4fa732c","tid":2362031,"uid":67186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T12:53:26.000Z","msg":"幫手推下"},{"pid":"40a9ec4b58baa7ad503f5e2697f39f4ca4b36bc9","tid":2362031,"uid":264529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T13:05:40.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"3c08b92acca5c8c63afa418b2af1479101b9b97f","tid":2362031,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T13:09:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a439e7d90f0775cfd5e1f09af07710e6842da44","tid":2362031,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2ce999f6c297b5b671f2f2471a37f6e7c4fa732c","tid":23